_sText:
The real name of the map is $2000$
It's my first map CS:Source, equivalent to the version CZ which I made some months ago.

Simply for fun ! That big killing off! 
Zones of purchase are between walls in the center of the map.
One AWP to the right and to the left of every Respawn, some HE along walls but also M4A1, MP5, AK-47 are available.
